## What Did NOT Change

- JSON token loader functions — untouched
- CRUD functions — untouched
- Save/Restore placeholder — untouched
- SQLite placeholder — untouched
- `tool-definitions.json` — untouched (Karen's input_schema mapping is handled inside ai-engine)

---

## One Thing to Watch

`aiEngineRouter` now takes `serverTarget` as the last arg ('local' or 'production').
This replaces the old `serverUrl` string. The router calls `mcpEngineStaging` internally
so it only needs the target name, not a full URL.

Old signature: `aiEngineRouter(userMessage, toolDefinitions, apiKey, serverUrl)`
New signature: `aiEngineRouter(userMessage, toolDefinitions, apiKey, provider, serverTarget)`

